"Change Set:		9627Collections-klc.329Collections-klc.329:Return both the minimum and maximum of the given collection in a single pass.Better (certainly reads better) implementation from Randal Schwartz.Collections-klc.328:Return both the minimum and maximum of the given collection in a single pass."!!Collection methodsFor: 'math functions' stamp: 'klc 3/7/2010 18:50'!minMax	"Scans for minimum and maximum in one pass returning the results as a two-element array"	| min max |	min := max := self anyOne.	self do: [ :each |		min := min min: each.		max := max max: each ].	^ Array with: min with: max! !